VERSION=X1

[COMMENT sphere_skillmenu]
SphereServer has a number of hardcoded skillmenu's, this file contains the softcoded component.
The purpose of these specific skillmenus is as follows:
sm_summon				= Triggered by the Magery "summoning" spell
sm_polymorph			= Triggered by the Magery Polymorph spell

[SKILLMENU sm_summon]
